quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  74,48,"Kho okhusabila khwomusabi shikhulibakhoonya shiosishiosi tawe."
  74,49,"Mana bali barieena abahelesinjia omukongo ameetsulisio kano?"
  74,50,"Opara mbu bo nitsisishili tsisundusibwe."
  74,51,"Tsilukhanga italanyi."
  74,52,"Mbu buli omundu mubo yenyanga ahebwe eshitabu shishie okhurula mwikulu."
  74,53,"Shikali kario tawe! Halali shibaritsanga aka Mwikulu tawe."
  74,54,"Shikali kario tawe! Toto kano ni ametsulisio."
  74,55,"Kho, ulia wenya, yetsulile."
  74,56,"Ne shibakhetsulila tawe okhuula Nyasaye achame. Ye niukhoyeshele okhuribwa, khandi ni Wobulesheli muno."
  75,1,"Nditsuba khuinyanga yeyinduukho."
  75,2,"Ne nditsuba khumwoyo kwa okhwifunaania."
  75,3,"Koo, omundu aparanga mbu shikhulikhung’asia halala ebikumba bibie tawe?"
  75,4,"Khulwa shina! Efwe khunyala okhura habwene tsinyali tsia tsinzala tsitsie."
  75,5,"Habula omundu yenyanga sa okhutsililila okhukhola amabii khutsinyanga tsili imbeli waye."
  75,6,"Arebanga mbu: “Iliba lina inyanga yeyindukho?”"
  75,7,"Mana olwa imoni iling’ang’aala."
  75,8,"Ne olwa omwesi kulitilana."
  75,9,"Ne olwa eliuba nende omwesi bilihambasibwa."
  75,10,"Inyanga eyo Omundu aliboola mbu: “Amelushilo kali yena?”"
  75,11,"Tawe! Wokhwilushila wosiwosi abulaho tawe!"
  75,12,"Inyanga eyo ewa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niiliba habundu wokhutong’ao."
  75,13,"Inyanga eyo omundu aliboolelwa kayaranjilisia nende kayamalilishia."
  75,14,"Halali buli omundu yemanyile omwene muno."
  75,15,"Kata narusia ebichila ebiinji."
  75,16,"Olabuyungubasilia (obufimbuli bwa Nyasaye) olulimi lulwo tawe, khulwokhubusooma lwangu lwangu tawe."
  75,17,"Toto kali khwifwe okhubukhuung’asia (mushilifu shishio) halala nende okhukhukhola obusome."
  75,18,"Kho nikhwakhabusooma, londelela okhusooma khwabuo."
  75,19,"Mana kali khwifwe okhubwinoosia (khwiwe)."